ActTerritorial Lands Act
SubjectWithdrawal from Disposal of the Subsurface Rights in Certain Tracts of Territorial Lands in the Northwest Territories (Nành´ Geenjit Gwitr´it Tigwaa´in/Working for the Land: Gwich’in Land Use Plan) Order
PrecisWITHDRAWAL FROM DISPOSAL OF THE SUBSURFACE RIGHTS IN CERTAIN TRACTS OF TERRITORIAL LANDS IN THE NORTHWEST TERRITORIES (NÀNH' GEENJIT GWITR'IT TIGWAA'IN / WORKING FOR THE LAND: GWICH'IN LAND USE PLAN) ORDER - A three-year extension of the interim land withdrawal is required to provide adequate time for the Gwich'in Land Use Planning Board time to amend the Land Use Plan if the amendment to the Land Use Plan is amended prior to the completion date the Order, the Order will be repealed.
RegistrationRegistration: SI/ 2011-0014 Publication Date: 2011-02-16
